a tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ea5m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1eeb ph\u00e2n v\u00e0o m\u00e1u. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng tr\u1ebb b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 ti\u00eau, \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ee5ng, Tinh b\u1ed9t h\u1eb9 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch ti\u00eau h\u00f3a, nhu\u1eadn tr\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u00e1o b\u00f3n \u1edf tr\u1ebb ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 do u\u1ed1ng \u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1. Khi m\u1eb9 cho b\u00e9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Tinh b\u1ed9t h\u1eb9, s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ti\u00eau h\u00f3a c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cung c\u1ea5p h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 g\u1ea5p 200 l\u1ea7n rau xanh, k\u00edch th\u00edch th\u00e0nh ru\u1ed9t gi\u00fap vi\u1ec7c &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":118,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/117"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=117"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/117\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/118"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/tinhbot.websiteviet.v